title: Side chair
medium: Fruitwood, mother-of-pearl, brass, white metal, cotton velvet upholstery
description: Small side chair with four slender tapered square legs; back consisting of low cross rail, narrow center splat and side rails with abrupt outward curve at top, repeated in crest rail where three large disks are centered.  Mother-of-pearl inlay; brass and white metal stringing on most elements.  Applied fruitwood cut out with brass stringing on center back splat; Seat upholstered in golden-yellow velvet.
name: Side chair
